reviews.text: It is at the basement of the building. Just like the other MX, there are different kinds of dishes for you to choose at all time round the clock. Be careful that there are not too much space in the shop and you may be hard to find a seat in the rush hours. Take away is a good choice that you can enjoy you lunch or dinner in this shop. The tea time is a good time and there will be seats available for you. May be you can see some customers having a nap in their seats!
I liked the food and the drinks. The price is really good too. My lunch piece was just 80hk dollars.
Many choice.of menu. Chicken curry little bit spicy for non asia people
Delicious and it suits people with different tastes
Easy and fast.. so many menu to choose.. yummy..affordable price

result.name: 美心 MX

reviews.text: 餸菜和飯份量小😓

It is at the basement of the building. Just like the other MX, there are different kinds of dishes for you to choose at all time round the clock. Be careful that there are not too much space in the shop and you may be hard to find a seat in the rush hours. Take away is a good choice that you can enjoy you lunch or dinner in this shop. The tea time is a good time and there will be seats available for you. May be you can see some customers having a nap in their seats!

多年沒有光顧美心快餐的早餐但今次真的被龍虾湯螺絲粉吸引了。
可惜買餐要排隊原來是因為兩位收银員在興高彩烈地傾談。
取餐處有效率，但禮貌上要向另外兩間對手學習學習。
慣性叫了薄牛扒煙肉熱啡加通粉。
冷的多士當然是"淋"的，薄牛扒煙肉只是不過不失也不好吃，而今日主角另加$11的龍虾湯螺絲粉竟然比不上麥記龍虾湯的味道，極之失敗!
這粒星是給收盤+抹抬唯一一個的姐姐。
相信下午茶炸雞髀熱啡外賣會是未來個人唯一會考慮的選擇。
